{Name}{}{Guard}
{Speech 1}{}{Predialogue installations}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{Answer text}
{Speech 2}{}{Stay away from other people's cars.@@Don't loiter at the lot.@@Shooting and fighting are forbidden. Troublemakers will be punished.@@What are you staring at@sex@|||?\n@@If you think you can steal someone else's car, you're wrong.@@I'm watching you.@@Take all your questions to the race organizers.@@This isn't a race, it's a circus - there are as many clowns here today as there are corpses around the reactor.\n@@Looking for your mommy?@@Don't block the view.@@Who do you take me for? Get out of here.@@Just wait until this show is over, then I'll deal with you.@@Do you want to ask something? Better keep quiet.@@The booth doesn't give out information.}
